data.description: Discover tranquility in this charming 3 bed, 3 bath townhouse nestled in a serene Monument neighborhood. Absorb the peace as you open your front door to a breathtaking natural scene. Gaze upon the beauty of an expansive open space, inviting you to immerse yourself in nature right from your doorstep, with a cup of coffee in hand. Embrace convenience with nearby amenities like shopping, the YMCA, ample trails, and Palmer Ridge High School. Step inside to find an open living area with an airy feel that is great for entertaining, including an eat-at breakfast bar. The spacious layout includes a large master bedroom with an ensuite bathroom featuring a double vanity. The convenience of an upstairs laundry room allows for less time doing chores and more time for fun! New features within the home include new interior paint, a brand-new garage door and hot water heater. Enjoy the perfect blend of comfort and accessibility in this delightful townhouse, where relaxation meets modern convenience.
